newDietryPlan

public DietryPlanData newDietryPlan(java.util.Date startdate,
                                    java.util.Date enddate,
                                    java.util.List<DietParameterData> dptd,
                                    java.util.List<java.lang.Double> parameterMaxValues,
                                    java.util.List<java.lang.Double> parameterMinValues,
                                    PatientBo activePatient,
                                    SystemUserBo activeUser)
                             throws NoPatientException,
                                    NoDateException,
                                    TimeIntersectionException,
                                    NoDietTreatmentException
Create a new dietry plan. Throws NoPatientException if the activePastient is null. Throws TimeIntersectionException if a dietplan for the timespan which is specified by start and end date is allready defined.

Parameters:
startdate - Startdate for the new Plan
dptd - List of DietparameterData
enddate - Enddate for the new Plan
parameterMaxValues - Max Values for the chosen parameters
parameterMinValues - Min Values for the chosen parameters
activePatient - Current active patient
activeUser -
Returns:
the new generated and validated dietplan
Throws:
NoPatientException - if no active patient exists
TimeIntersectionException - if illegal timespan is defined by start and enddate
NoDateException - if start or enddate is null
NoDietTreatmentException - if active patient has no treatment
